Global Nutrition Consulting Services Market Insights
Nutrition Consulting Services Market size was valued at USD 9.6 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 15.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Nutrition Consulting Services Market Overview
The global nutrition consulting services market is projected to grow significantly in the coming years, driven by increasing health awareness and the rising demand for personalized diet plans and wellness solutions. The market value is expected to reach $9.5 billion by 2030, reflecting a steady CAGR. This growth is primarily fueled by an increase in chronic diseases, an aging population, and a growing preference for preventive healthcare. Additionally, the rise of digital platforms for nutrition consulting services is opening new avenues for service providers, enabling them to reach a global audience.

